Subject: [PATCH v3] tee: add support for application-based session login
 methods
Message-ID: <20201005173136.6c220768@akathisia>
X-Mailer: Claws Mail 3.17.5 (GTK+ 2.24.32; x86_64-pc-linux-gnu)
MIME-Version: 1.0
